WEBVTT

1
00:00:59.309 --> 00:01:01.270
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[THUNDER RUMBLING]</font>

2
00:01:06.316 --> 00:01:07.776
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[BABY COOS]</font>

3
00:01:09.444 --> 00:01:11.989
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">DILIOS:
<i>When the boy was born…</i></font>

4
00:01:12.823 --> 00:01:14.950
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…like all Spartans, he was inspected.</i></font>

5
00:01:16.743 --> 00:01:21.373
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>If he'd been small or puny
or sickly or misshapen…</i></font>

6
00:01:21.540 --> 00:01:23.875
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…he would have been discarded.</i></font>

7
00:01:31.008 --> 00:01:36.680
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>From the time he could stand,
he was baptized in the fire of combat.</i></font>

8
00:01:38.432 --> 00:01:40.017
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[GRUNTING]</font>

9
00:01:58.744 --> 00:02:02.414
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Taught never to retreat,
never to surrender.</i></font>

10
00:02:02.581 --> 00:02:07.461
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Taught that death on the battlefield
in service to Sparta…</i></font>

11
00:02:07.669 --> 00:02:10.964
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…was the greatest glory
he could achieve in his life.</i></font>

12
00:02:26.104 --> 00:02:30.651
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>At age 7, as is customary in Sparta…</i></font>

13
00:02:30.817 --> 00:02:35.906
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…the boy was taken from his mother
and plunged into a world of violence.</i></font>

14
00:02:36.073 --> 00:02:37.074
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[GRUNTING]</font>

15
00:02:37.240 --> 00:02:41.328
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Manufactured by 300 years
of Spartan warrior society…</i></font>

16
00:02:42.371 --> 00:02:46.667
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…to create the finest soldiers
the world has ever known.</i></font>

17
00:02:46.833 --> 00:02:51.421
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>The</i> agoge, <i>as it's called,
forces the boy to fight.</i></font>

18
00:02:51.588 --> 00:02:55.217
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Starves them, forces them to steal…</i></font>

19
00:02:55.384 --> 00:02:59.763
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…and if necessary, to kill.</i></font>

20
00:03:00.806 --> 00:03:03.809
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>By rod and lash the boy was punished…</i></font>

21
00:03:03.975 --> 00:03:07.270
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…taught to show no pain, no mercy.</i></font>

22
00:03:08.980 --> 00:03:12.484
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Constantly tested, tossed into the wild.</i></font>

23
00:03:12.651 --> 00:03:17.948
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Left to pit his wits and will
against nature's fury.</i></font>

24
00:03:18.323 --> 00:03:20.534
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>It was his initiation…</i></font>

25
00:03:20.701 --> 00:03:23.286
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…his time in the wild…</i></font>

26
00:03:23.453 --> 00:03:27.958
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…for he would return to his people
a Spartan…</i></font>

27
00:03:28.125 --> 00:03:30.252
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…or not at all.</i></font>

28
00:03:30.711 --> 00:03:31.920
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[WOLF GROWLING]</font>

29
00:03:52.566 --> 00:03:55.444
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>The wolf begins to circle the boy.</i></font>

30
00:03:55.610 --> 00:03:58.029
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Claws of black steel…</i></font>

31
00:03:58.196 --> 00:04:00.449
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…fur as dark night.</i></font>

32
00:04:00.949 --> 00:04:02.284
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Eyes glowing red…</i></font>

33
00:04:02.451 --> 00:04:06.371
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…jewels from the pit of hell itself.</i></font>

34
00:04:15.130 --> 00:04:19.134
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>The giant wolf sniffing…</i></font>

35
00:04:19.301 --> 00:04:22.345
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…savoring the scent of the meal to come.</i></font>

36
00:04:22.846 --> 00:04:24.389
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[SNARLING]</font>

37
00:04:35.275 --> 00:04:36.610
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[WOLF WHIMPERS]</font>

38
00:04:37.027 --> 00:04:38.361
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[WOLF HOWLING]</font>

39
00:04:46.536 --> 00:04:48.038
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>It's not fear that grips him…</i></font>

40
00:04:48.663 --> 00:04:51.833
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…only a heightened sense of things.</i></font>

41
00:04:52.167 --> 00:04:55.545
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>The cold air in his lungs.</i></font>

42
00:04:56.087 --> 00:04:59.424
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Windswept pines
moving against the coming night.</i></font>

43
00:05:01.343 --> 00:05:03.053
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[HOWLING]</font>

44
00:05:07.432 --> 00:05:09.851
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>His hands are steady.</i></font>

45
00:05:10.018 --> 00:05:12.270
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>His form…</i></font>

46
00:05:12.437 --> 00:05:14.564
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…perfect.</i></font>

47
00:05:40.340 --> 00:05:43.093
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>And so the boy, given up for dead…</i></font>

48
00:05:43.260 --> 00:05:47.973
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…returns to his people,
to sacred Sparta, a king!</i></font>

49
00:05:48.431 --> 00:05:50.934
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Our king, Leonidas!</font>

50
00:05:51.101 --> 00:05:52.519
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[SPARTANS CHANTING]</font>

51
00:05:58.066 --> 00:06:01.820
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">It's been more than 30 years
since the wolf and the winter cold.</font>

52
00:06:03.238 --> 00:06:07.534
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">And now, as then, a beast approaches.</font>

53
00:06:07.701 --> 00:06:12.622
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Patient and confident,
savoring the meal to come.</font>

54
00:06:13.290 --> 00:06:16.585
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">But this beast
is made of men and horses…</font>

55
00:06:16.751 --> 00:06:19.546
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…swords and spears.</font>

56
00:06:19.754 --> 00:06:24.718
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">An army of slaves, vast beyond imagining,
ready to devour tiny Greece.</font>

57
00:06:25.051 --> 00:06:29.806
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Ready to snuff out the world's
one hope for reason and justice.</font>

58
00:06:32.559 --> 00:06:35.312
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">A beast approaches…</font>

59
00:06:38.106 --> 00:06:43.653
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…and it was King Leonidas himself
who provoked it.</font>

60
00:07:37.374 --> 00:07:39.042
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[HORSE NEIGHING]</font>

61
00:07:54.265 --> 00:07:55.266
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">LEONIDAS:
That's it.</font>

62
00:07:55.433 --> 00:07:56.434
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[PLEISTARCHOS GRUNTING]</font>

63
00:07:56.601 --> 00:08:01.314
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">LEONIDAS: Now, the more you sweat
here, the less you'll bleed in battle.</font>

64
00:08:02.524 --> 00:08:04.984
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">My father taught me…</font>

65
00:08:05.151 --> 00:08:07.612
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…that fear is always a constant.</font>

66
00:08:07.779 --> 00:08:09.322
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">But accepting it…</font>

67
00:08:09.698 --> 00:08:10.824
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…makes you stronger.</font>

68
00:08:10.991 --> 00:08:12.367
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">My queen.</font>

69
00:08:12.534 --> 00:08:15.370
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">A Persian emissary awaits Leonidas.</font>

70
00:08:17.914 --> 00:08:19.290
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">In the end…</font>

71
00:08:19.457 --> 00:08:23.044
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…a Spartan's true strength
is the warrior next to him.</font>

72
00:08:23.795 --> 00:08:28.299
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">So give respect and honor to him,
and it will be returned to you.</font>

73
00:08:28.842 --> 00:08:30.343
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">First…</font>

74
00:08:31.094 --> 00:08:34.055
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">- …you fight with your head.
- Then you fight with your heart.</font>

75
00:08:36.391 --> 00:08:38.101
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">What is it?</font>

76
00:08:38.309 --> 00:08:40.186
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">A Persian messenger awaits you.</font>

77
00:08:42.480 --> 00:08:43.940
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Do not forget today's lesson.</font>

78
00:08:44.107 --> 00:08:46.818
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">- Respect and honor.
LEONIDAS: Respect and honor.</font>

79
00:09:02.333 --> 00:09:06.796
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Councilman Theron.
You found yourself needed, for once.</font>

80
00:09:07.881 --> 00:09:10.800
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">My king and queen,
I was just entertaining your guests.</font>

81
00:09:11.009 --> 00:09:12.260
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I'm sure.</font>

82
00:09:13.470 --> 00:09:15.305
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Before you speak, Persian…</font>

83
00:09:15.472 --> 00:09:18.767
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…know that in Sparta everyone,
even a king's messenger…</font>

84
00:09:18.933 --> 00:09:21.519
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…is held accountable
for the words of his voice.</font>

85
00:09:22.520 --> 00:09:25.273
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Now, what message do you bring?</font>

86
00:09:26.357 --> 00:09:28.818
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Earth and water.</font>

87
00:09:31.112 --> 00:09:34.741
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You rode all the way from Persia
for earth and water?</font>

88
00:09:36.326 --> 00:09:40.205
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Do not be coy or stupid, Persian.
You can afford neither in Sparta.</font>

89
00:09:40.705 --> 00:09:43.166
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">What makes this woman
think she can speak among men?</font>

90
00:09:43.333 --> 00:09:46.169
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Because only Spartan women
give birth to real men.</font>

91
00:09:47.670 --> 00:09:51.299
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Let us walk to cool our tongues.</font>

92
00:09:53.885 --> 00:09:57.055
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">If you value your lives
over your complete annihilation…</font>

93
00:09:57.222 --> 00:09:58.890
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…listen carefully, Leonidas.</font>

94
00:09:59.057 --> 00:10:03.770
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Xerxes conquers and controls
everything he rests his eyes upon.</font>

95
00:10:03.937 --> 00:10:07.023
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">He leads an army so massive,
it shakes the ground with its march.</font>

96
00:10:07.190 --> 00:10:09.901
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">So vast, it drinks the rivers dry.</font>

97
00:10:10.068 --> 00:10:13.071
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">All the God-King Xerxes requires is this:</font>

98
00:10:13.404 --> 00:10:16.658
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">A simple offering of earth and water…</font>

99
00:10:16.825 --> 00:10:20.995
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…a token of Sparta's submission
to the will of Xerxes.</font>

100
00:10:32.048 --> 00:10:34.217
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Submission.</font>

101
00:10:36.386 --> 00:10:38.304
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Now, that's a bit of a problem.</font>

102
00:10:38.721 --> 00:10:39.973
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">See, rumor has it…</font>

103
00:10:40.139 --> 00:10:42.767
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…the Athenians
have already turned you down.</font>

104
00:10:43.685 --> 00:10:48.898
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">And if those philosophers and boy-lovers
have found that kind of nerve, then…</font>

105
00:10:49.065 --> 00:10:53.319
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">- We must be diplomatic.
- And, of course, Spartans…</font>

106
00:10:54.362 --> 00:10:56.406
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…have their reputation to consider.</font>

107
00:10:56.573 --> 00:11:00.618
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Choose your next words carefully,
Leonidas.</font>

108
00:11:00.869 --> 00:11:03.496
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">They may be your last as king.</font>

109
00:11:43.953 --> 00:11:47.290
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">LEONIDAS:
<i>"Earth and water".</i></font>

110
00:11:52.545 --> 00:11:54.631
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Madman. You're a madman.</font>

111
00:11:54.797 --> 00:11:56.466
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Earth and water.</font>

112
00:11:56.841 --> 00:11:59.010
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You'll find plenty of both down there.</font>

113
00:11:59.302 --> 00:12:02.722
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">No man, Persian or Greek,
no man threatens a messenger.</font>

114
00:12:03.181 --> 00:12:08.144
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You bring the crowns and heads
of conquered kings to my city steps.</font>

115
00:12:08.311 --> 00:12:10.396
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You insult my queen.</font>

116
00:12:10.563 --> 00:12:14.317
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You threaten my people
with slavery and death.</font>

117
00:12:14.484 --> 00:12:17.403
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Oh, I've chosen my words carefully,
Persian.</font>

118
00:12:17.570 --> 00:12:19.530
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Perhaps you should have done the same.</font>

119
00:12:19.697 --> 00:12:23.368
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">This is blasphemy. This is madness!</font>

120
00:12:40.760 --> 00:12:42.845
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Madness?</font>

121
00:12:43.471 --> 00:12:45.598
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">This is Sparta!</font>

122
00:12:46.057 --> 00:12:47.850
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[MESSENGER SCREAMING]</font>

123
00:12:57.944 --> 00:12:59.445
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[PEOPLE SCREAMING]</font>

124
00:13:47.702 --> 00:13:48.911
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[GRUNTING]</font>

125
00:13:52.373 --> 00:13:53.458
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[THUNDER RUMBLING]</font>

126
00:14:12.101 --> 00:14:14.479
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">EPHOR 1:
Welcome, Leonidas.</font>

127
00:14:15.104 --> 00:14:18.274
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">We have been expecting you.</font>

128
00:14:24.739 --> 00:14:30.078
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">DILIOS:
<i>The ephors, priests to the old gods.</i></font>

129
00:14:30.453 --> 00:14:32.789
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Inbred swine.</i></font>

130
00:14:32.955 --> 00:14:35.750
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>More creature than man.</i></font>

131
00:14:36.167 --> 00:14:41.631
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Creatures whom even Leonidas
must bribe and beg.</i></font>

132
00:14:42.465 --> 00:14:47.303
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>For no Spartan king has gone to war
without the ephors' blessing.</i></font>

133
00:14:48.971 --> 00:14:53.059
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">LEONIDAS: <i>The Persians claim
their forces number in the millions.</i></font>

134
00:14:53.684 --> 00:14:56.979
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I hope, for our sake, they exaggerate.</font>

135
00:14:57.438 --> 00:15:01.651
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">But there's no question, we face
the most massive army ever assembled.</font>

136
00:15:01.901 --> 00:15:05.238
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Before your plan is heard…</font>

137
00:15:05.404 --> 00:15:07.657
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…what do you offer?</font>

138
00:15:17.208 --> 00:15:21.546
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">We will use our superior fighting skills…</font>

139
00:15:21.712 --> 00:15:25.800
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…and the terrain of Greece herself
to destroy them.</font>

140
00:15:25.967 --> 00:15:28.803
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">We will march north to the coast,
where I will make sure…</font>

141
00:15:28.970 --> 00:15:33.850
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">It is August, Leonidas.
The full moon approaches.</font>

142
00:15:34.225 --> 00:15:37.437
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">EPH0R2:
The sacred and ancient festival.</font>

143
00:15:37.603 --> 00:15:41.691
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Sparta wages no war
at the time of the Carneia.</font>

144
00:15:41.858 --> 00:15:43.484
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Sparta will burn!</font>

145
00:15:43.901 --> 00:15:45.445
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Her men will die at arms…</font>

146
00:15:45.611 --> 00:15:49.282
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…and her women and children
will be slaves or worse.</font>

147
00:15:51.409 --> 00:15:56.497
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Now, we will block
the Persian coastal assault…</font>

148
00:15:56.789 --> 00:15:59.083
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…by rebuilding the great Phocian Wall.</font>

149
00:15:59.250 --> 00:16:03.963
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">And from there, we will funnel them into
the mountain pass we call the Hot Gates.</font>

150
00:16:04.130 --> 00:16:08.509
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Now, in that narrow corridor,
their numbers will count for nothing.</font>

151
00:16:08.676 --> 00:16:11.262
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">And wave after wave of Persian attack…</font>

152
00:16:11.429 --> 00:16:15.391
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…will smash against Spartan shields.</font>

153
00:16:15.933 --> 00:16:20.229
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Xerxes' losses will be so great,
his men so demoralized…</font>

154
00:16:20.396 --> 00:16:24.817
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…he will have no choice
but to abandon his campaign.</font>

155
00:16:24.984 --> 00:16:27.695
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">We must consult the oracle.</font>

156
00:16:28.404 --> 00:16:30.990
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Trust the gods, Leonidas.</font>

157
00:16:31.157 --> 00:16:34.493
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I'd prefer you trusted your reason.</font>

158
00:16:34.660 --> 00:16:36.704
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Your blasphemies…</font>

159
00:16:36.871 --> 00:16:41.250
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…have cost us quite enough already.</font>

160
00:16:41.959 --> 00:16:45.004
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Don't compound them.</font>

161
00:16:47.089 --> 00:16:51.886
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">We will consult the oracle.</font>

162
00:16:54.013 --> 00:16:56.515
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">DILIOS:
<i>Diseased old mystics.</i></font>

163
00:16:57.517 --> 00:17:02.146
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Worthless remnants of a time
before Sparta's ascent from darkness.</i></font>

164
00:17:02.480 --> 00:17:05.775
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Remnants of a senseless tradition.</i></font>

165
00:17:05.942 --> 00:17:10.279
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Tradition even Leonidas cannot defy…</i></font>

166
00:17:10.446 --> 00:17:14.867
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…for he must respect
the word of the ephors.</i></font>

167
00:17:15.034 --> 00:17:16.953
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>That is the law.</i></font>

168
00:17:19.997 --> 00:17:24.335
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>And no Spartan, subject or citizen,
man or woman…</i></font>

169
00:17:24.502 --> 00:17:28.547
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…slave or king, is above the law.</i></font>

170
00:18:03.416 --> 00:18:07.670
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>The ephors choose only
the most beautiful Spartan girls…</i></font>

171
00:18:07.837 --> 00:18:10.339
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…to live among them as oracles.</i></font>

172
00:18:10.506 --> 00:18:13.801
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Their beauty is their curse…</i></font>

173
00:18:13.968 --> 00:18:17.763
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…for the old wretches
have the needs of men…</i></font>

174
00:18:18.764 --> 00:18:21.684
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…and souls as black as hell.</i></font>

175
00:18:21.851 --> 00:18:23.603
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[ORACLE WHISPERING
IN FOREIGN LANGUAGE]</font>

176
00:18:25.855 --> 00:18:29.025
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">EPHOR:
"Pray to the winds…</font>

177
00:18:31.527 --> 00:18:33.738
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…Sparta will fall.</font>

178
00:18:36.699 --> 00:18:40.369
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">All Greece will fall.</font>

179
00:18:42.538 --> 00:18:46.208
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Trust not in men…</font>

180
00:18:48.210 --> 00:18:51.505
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…honor the gods.</font>

181
00:18:55.217 --> 00:18:58.888
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Honor the Carneia".</font>

182
00:19:00.723 --> 00:19:04.310
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">DILIOS:
<i>The king's climb down is harder.</i></font>

183
00:19:04.477 --> 00:19:07.396
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Pompous, inbred swine.</i></font>

184
00:19:07.563 --> 00:19:10.775
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Worthless, diseased, rotten…</i></font>

185
00:19:10.941 --> 00:19:12.985
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…corrupt.</i></font>

186
00:19:16.364 --> 00:19:19.992
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">THERON: Truly, you're
in the god-king's favor now…</font>

187
00:19:20.576 --> 00:19:22.661
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…O wise and holy men.</font>

188
00:19:22.953 --> 00:19:24.413
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Yes.</font>

189
00:19:24.580 --> 00:19:29.543
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">And when Sparta burns,
you shall bathe in gold.</font>

190
00:19:29.710 --> 00:19:32.296
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Fresh oracles shall be delivered to you…</font>

191
00:19:32.755 --> 00:19:34.173
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…daily…</font>

192
00:19:34.340 --> 00:19:38.135
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…from every corner of the empire.</font>

193
00:19:42.223 --> 00:19:43.432
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[CHUCKLING]</font>

194
00:20:13.796 --> 00:20:17.383
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">GORGO: Your lips can finish
what your fingers have started.</font>

195
00:20:20.511 --> 00:20:22.972
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Or has the oracle robbed you
of your desire as well?</font>

196
00:20:24.515 --> 00:20:27.560
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">It would take more than the words
of a drunken adolescent girl…</font>

197
00:20:27.727 --> 00:20:29.437
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…to rob me of my desire for you.</font>

198
00:20:33.607 --> 00:20:35.067
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Then why so distant?</font>

199
00:20:38.195 --> 00:20:40.197
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Because it seems…</font>

200
00:20:40.364 --> 00:20:46.328
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…though a slave and captive
of lecherous old men…</font>

201
00:20:46.662 --> 00:20:49.874
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…the oracle's words
could set fire to all that I love.</font>

202
00:20:50.040 --> 00:20:53.711
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">So that is why my king loses sleep
and is forced from the warmth of his bed?</font>

203
00:20:56.672 --> 00:21:01.010
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">There's only one woman's words that
should affect the mood of my husband.</font>

204
00:21:01.844 --> 00:21:03.429
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Those are mine.</font>

205
00:21:03.804 --> 00:21:05.181
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[CHUCKLES]</font>

206
00:21:07.600 --> 00:21:10.019
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Then what must a king do
to save his world…</font>

207
00:21:10.186 --> 00:21:14.607
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…when the very laws he is sworn
to protect force him to do nothing?</font>

208
00:21:17.526 --> 00:21:20.863
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">It is not a question
of what a Spartan citizen should do…</font>

209
00:21:21.030 --> 00:21:23.908
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…nor a husband, nor a king.</font>

210
00:21:24.533 --> 00:21:27.244
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Instead ask yourself, my dearest love…</font>

211
00:21:28.871 --> 00:21:30.873
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…what should a free man do?</font>

212
00:22:36.355 --> 00:22:40.526
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">- Is this all of them?
- As you ordered. Three hundred.</font>

213
00:22:41.527 --> 00:22:44.822
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">All with born sons to carry on their name.</font>

214
00:22:55.583 --> 00:22:56.917
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">We are with you, sire.</font>

215
00:22:57.293 --> 00:22:59.420
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">For Sparta. For freedom.</font>

216
00:22:59.587 --> 00:23:01.547
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">To the death.</font>

217
00:23:12.349 --> 00:23:14.018
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">LEONIDAS:
He is your son.</font>

218
00:23:14.810 --> 00:23:17.730
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">He is too young
to have felt a woman's warmth.</font>

219
00:23:17.896 --> 00:23:21.859
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I have others to replace him.
Astinos is as brave and ready as any.</font>

220
00:23:22.192 --> 00:23:26.238
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">No younger than we were the first time
you stood next to me in battle.</font>

221
00:23:29.992 --> 00:23:32.161
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You are a good friend…</font>

222
00:23:32.328 --> 00:23:35.831
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…but a better captain, there is none.</font>

223
00:23:41.337 --> 00:23:43.255
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">COUNCILMAN:
My good king.</font>

224
00:23:44.173 --> 00:23:47.509
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">My good king, the oracle has spoken.</font>

225
00:23:47.676 --> 00:23:50.554
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">The ephors have spoken.
There must be no march.</font>

226
00:23:50.721 --> 00:23:52.514
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">It is the law, my lord.</font>

227
00:23:52.681 --> 00:23:56.685
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">- The Spartan army must not go to war.
- Nor shall it.</font>

228
00:23:57.603 --> 00:23:59.188
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I've issued no such orders.</font>

229
00:23:59.563 --> 00:24:03.108
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I'm here just taking a stroll,
stretching my legs.</font>

230
00:24:03.359 --> 00:24:08.530
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">These 300 men
are my personal bodyguard.</font>

231
00:24:08.781 --> 00:24:10.950
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Our army will stay in Sparta.</font>

232
00:24:11.533 --> 00:24:12.868
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Where will you go?</font>

233
00:24:15.871 --> 00:24:18.082
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I hadn't really thought about it…</font>

234
00:24:18.874 --> 00:24:21.043
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…but now that you ask…</font>

235
00:24:21.210 --> 00:24:23.962
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…I suppose I'll head north.</font>

236
00:24:25.381 --> 00:24:26.507
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">The Hot Gates?</font>

237
00:24:29.134 --> 00:24:31.553
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">CAPTAIN:
Move out!</font>

238
00:24:31.720 --> 00:24:33.806
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Move out!</font>

239
00:24:34.932 --> 00:24:36.558
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">What shall we do?</font>

240
00:24:38.060 --> 00:24:39.395
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">What can we do?</font>

241
00:24:40.104 --> 00:24:41.855
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">What can you do?</font>

242
00:24:44.900 --> 00:24:48.737
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Sparta will need sons.</font>

243
00:25:36.493 --> 00:25:38.245
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Spartan!</font>

244
00:25:47.504 --> 00:25:48.756
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Yes, milady?</font>

245
00:26:04.813 --> 00:26:07.149
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Come back with your shield…</font>

246
00:26:08.066 --> 00:26:09.485
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…or on it.</font>

247
00:26:10.986 --> 00:26:12.321
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Yes, milady.</font>

248
00:26:20.829 --> 00:26:23.165
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">DILIOS:
<i>"Goodbye, my love".</i></font>

249
00:26:23.791 --> 00:26:26.001
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>He doesn't say it.</i></font>

250
00:26:26.502 --> 00:26:28.712
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>There's no room for softness…</i></font>

251
00:26:28.879 --> 00:26:30.881
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…not in Sparta.</i></font>

252
00:26:31.048 --> 00:26:33.842
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>No place for weakness.</i></font>

253
00:26:37.346 --> 00:26:41.517
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Only the hard and strong
may call themselves Spartans.</i></font>

254
00:26:42.351 --> 00:26:46.855
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Only the hard. Only the strong.</i></font>

255
00:27:15.342 --> 00:27:17.219
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>We march…</i></font>

256
00:27:17.886 --> 00:27:23.392
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…for our lands, for our families,
for our freedoms.</i></font>

257
00:27:24.184 --> 00:27:26.353
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>We march.</i></font>

258
00:27:28.063 --> 00:27:29.731
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">LEONIDAS:
Daxos.</font>

259
00:27:29.898 --> 00:27:33.318
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">- What a pleasant surprise.
- This morning's full of surprises, Leonidas.</font>

260
00:27:33.485 --> 00:27:35.904
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">- We've been tricked.
- Can't be more than a hundred.</font>

261
00:27:36.071 --> 00:27:38.282
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">BAKER: This is a surprise.
DAXOS: Silence.</font>

262
00:27:38.740 --> 00:27:40.701
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">ARCADIAN:
This isn't their army.</font>

263
00:27:40.868 --> 00:27:45.038
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">We heard Sparta was on the warpath
and we were eager to join forces.</font>

264
00:27:45.706 --> 00:27:49.793
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">If it is blood you seek,
you are welcome to join us.</font>

265
00:27:50.127 --> 00:27:53.380
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">But you bring only this handful
of soldiers against Xerxes?</font>

266
00:27:53.547 --> 00:27:57.134
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I see I was wrong to expect Sparta's
commitment to at least match our own.</font>

267
00:27:58.302 --> 00:28:00.137
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Doesn't it?</font>

268
00:28:01.597 --> 00:28:03.265
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You, there.</font>

269
00:28:03.765 --> 00:28:04.933
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">What is your profession?</font>

270
00:28:05.475 --> 00:28:07.603
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I'm a potter, sir.</font>

271
00:28:08.770 --> 00:28:12.566
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">And you, Arcadian.
What is your profession?</font>

272
00:28:12.941 --> 00:28:16.361
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">- Sculptor, sir.
- Sculptor.</font>

273
00:28:16.737 --> 00:28:18.655
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">- And you?
- Blacksmith.</font>

274
00:28:23.327 --> 00:28:26.622
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Spartans! What is your profession?</font>

275
00:28:27.122 --> 00:28:28.498
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[SPARTANS CHANTING]</font>

276
00:28:33.795 --> 00:28:35.756
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You see, old friend?</font>

277
00:28:35.923 --> 00:28:38.800
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I brought more soldiers than you did.</font>

278
00:28:48.769 --> 00:28:50.562
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">DILIOS:
<i>No sleep tonight…</i></font>

279
00:28:51.647 --> 00:28:54.107
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…not for the king.</i></font>

280
00:28:54.274 --> 00:28:56.485
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>All his 40 years
have been a straight road…</i></font>

281
00:28:56.652 --> 00:29:00.238
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…to this one gleaming moment
in destiny…</i></font>

282
00:29:00.405 --> 00:29:03.158
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…this one radiant clash
of shield and spear…</i></font>

283
00:29:03.325 --> 00:29:06.954
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…sword and bone, and flesh and blood.</i></font>

284
00:29:08.664 --> 00:29:10.457
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>His only regret…</i></font>

285
00:29:10.624 --> 00:29:14.336
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…is that he has so few to sacrifice.</i></font>

286
00:29:35.649 --> 00:29:37.651
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">We're being followed.</font>

287
00:29:42.698 --> 00:29:44.866
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">It has followed us since Sparta.</font>

288
00:29:49.830 --> 00:29:52.833
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">STELIOS:
My king! Look!</font>

289
00:30:13.770 --> 00:30:15.230
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">STELIOS:
What happened here?</font>

290
00:30:15.814 --> 00:30:17.149
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Where are all the people?</font>

291
00:30:18.233 --> 00:30:19.943
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Persians.</font>

292
00:30:20.110 --> 00:30:21.903
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I put their number at around 20.</font>

293
00:30:24.281 --> 00:30:25.657
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">A scouting party.</font>

294
00:30:29.036 --> 00:30:30.537
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">But these footprints…</font>

295
00:30:35.000 --> 00:30:36.334
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[CLATTERING]</font>

296
00:30:41.923 --> 00:30:43.383
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">STELIOS:
Behind us!</font>

297
00:30:57.439 --> 00:30:58.648
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Child!</font>

298
00:31:31.640 --> 00:31:34.351
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">CHILD [WHISPERING]:
It's quiet now.</font>

299
00:31:34.810 --> 00:31:36.645
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">They…</font>

300
00:31:36.978 --> 00:31:41.024
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">They came with beasts
from the blackness.</font>

301
00:31:42.609 --> 00:31:44.861
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">With their claws and fangs…</font>

302
00:31:45.028 --> 00:31:47.280
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…they grabbed them.</font>

303
00:31:48.156 --> 00:31:50.325
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Everyone…</font>

304
00:31:51.326 --> 00:31:53.412
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…but me.</font>

305
00:32:05.674 --> 00:32:07.217
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">DILIOS:
The villagers.</font>

306
00:32:07.759 --> 00:32:09.678
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I found them.</font>

307
00:32:21.189 --> 00:32:24.025
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Have the gods no mercy?</font>

308
00:32:25.193 --> 00:32:27.195
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">We are doomed.</font>

309
00:32:27.362 --> 00:32:30.031
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Quiet yourself.</font>

310
00:32:33.410 --> 00:32:38.665
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">The child speaks of the Persian ghosts,
known from the ancient times.</font>

311
00:32:39.541 --> 00:32:42.210
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">They are the hunters of men's souls.</font>

312
00:32:43.253 --> 00:32:45.881
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">They cannot be killed or defeated.</font>

313
00:32:46.506 --> 00:32:50.677
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Not this darkness. Not these Immortals.</font>

314
00:32:52.846 --> 00:32:55.056
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Immortals?</font>

315
00:32:55.348 --> 00:32:58.393
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">We'll put their name to the test.</font>

316
00:33:20.457 --> 00:33:23.251
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">DILIOS:
<i>Into the Hot Gates we march.</i></font>

317
00:33:23.418 --> 00:33:26.713
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Into that narrow corridor we march…</i></font>

318
00:33:26.880 --> 00:33:29.132
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…where Xerxes' numbers
count for nothing.</i></font>

319
00:33:30.300 --> 00:33:34.262
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Spartans, citizen-soldiers, freed slaves.</i></font>

320
00:33:34.429 --> 00:33:36.306
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Brave Greeks, all.</i></font>

321
00:33:37.307 --> 00:33:40.435
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Brothers, fathers, sons…</i></font>

322
00:33:40.602 --> 00:33:42.604
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…we march.</i></font>

323
00:33:43.271 --> 00:33:47.442
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>For honor's sake, for duty's sake,
for glory's sake, we march.</i></font>

324
00:33:47.609 --> 00:33:50.737
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Look! Persians.</font>

325
00:33:55.867 --> 00:33:59.621
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">DILIOS:
<i>Into hell's mouth we march.</i></font>

326
00:34:06.127 --> 00:34:07.337
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[THUNDER RUMBLING]</font>

327
00:34:08.630 --> 00:34:10.715
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Let's watch these motherless dogs…</font>

328
00:34:10.966 --> 00:34:15.011
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…as they're embraced by the loving arms
of Greece herself. Come.</font>

329
00:34:17.806 --> 00:34:19.516
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">True.</font>

330
00:34:23.728 --> 00:34:26.189
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">It does look like rain.</font>

331
00:34:29.484 --> 00:34:32.737
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">DILIOS:
<i>Zeus stabs the sky with thunderbolts…</i></font>

332
00:34:33.029 --> 00:34:37.075
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…and batters the Persian ships
with hurricane wind.</i></font>

333
00:34:38.201 --> 00:34:40.662
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Glorious.</i></font>

334
00:34:42.163 --> 00:34:43.832
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[SHOUTING]</font>

335
00:34:52.924 --> 00:34:55.802
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">DILI OS: <i>Only one among us
keeps his Spartan reserve.</i></font>

336
00:35:01.725 --> 00:35:03.685
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Only he.</i></font>

337
00:35:03.852 --> 00:35:06.313
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Only our king.</i></font>

338
00:35:23.705 --> 00:35:25.665
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">My queen?</font>

339
00:35:30.837 --> 00:35:32.172
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">My queen…</font>

340
00:35:32.339 --> 00:35:35.675
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…the courtyard is a more fitting place
for a married woman.</font>

341
00:35:35.842 --> 00:35:37.510
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I'm afraid gossip and protocol…</font>

342
00:35:37.677 --> 00:35:40.221
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…are the least of my worries now,
councilman.</font>

343
00:35:41.890 --> 00:35:43.725
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Is such secrecy needed?</font>

344
00:35:43.892 --> 00:35:46.561
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">How am I to trust beyond the walls
of my own home?</font>

345
00:35:46.728 --> 00:35:50.440
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Even here, Theron has eyes and ears
which fuel Sparta with doubt and fear.</font>

346
00:35:50.857 --> 00:35:54.235
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You speak as if all Sparta
conspires against you.</font>

347
00:35:54.903 --> 00:35:56.946
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I wish it were only against me.</font>

348
00:35:59.574 --> 00:36:03.078
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">LOYALIST: Many on our council
would vote to give all we have…</font>

349
00:36:03.244 --> 00:36:05.121
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…and follow Leonidas…</font>

350
00:36:05.455 --> 00:36:07.415
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…but you must show them favor.</font>

351
00:36:09.751 --> 00:36:12.212
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">And you can arrange for me
to speak to the council?</font>

352
00:36:12.379 --> 00:36:14.798
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">If it is reason they want,
I will let them know.</font>

353
00:36:14.964 --> 00:36:17.092
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">LOYALIST:
Know what, my queen?</font>

354
00:36:17.467 --> 00:36:19.469
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Freedom isn't free at all.</font>

355
00:36:19.636 --> 00:36:22.972
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">That it comes with the highest of costs,
the cost of blood.</font>

356
00:36:25.266 --> 00:36:27.894
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I will do my best to gather our council.</font>

357
00:36:28.311 --> 00:36:32.148
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">And its chamber
shall be filled with your voice.</font>

358
00:36:32.482 --> 00:36:34.317
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">GORGO: I'm in your debt.
- No.</font>

359
00:36:34.651 --> 00:36:38.822
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Leonidas is my king as well as yours.</font>

360
00:37:03.638 --> 00:37:05.473
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I saw those ships smash on the rocks.</font>

361
00:37:06.599 --> 00:37:07.976
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">How can this be?</font>

362
00:37:08.143 --> 00:37:11.438
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">We saw but a fraction of the monster
that is Xerxes' army.</font>

363
00:37:12.105 --> 00:37:14.482
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">DAXOS:
There can be no victory here.</font>

364
00:37:18.445 --> 00:37:20.155
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Why do you smile?</font>

365
00:37:21.823 --> 00:37:23.783
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Arcadian…</font>

366
00:37:23.950 --> 00:37:26.995
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…I have fought countless times…</font>

367
00:37:27.245 --> 00:37:29.914
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…yet I've never met an adversary
who could offer me…</font>

368
00:37:30.081 --> 00:37:32.250
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…what we Spartans
call "a beautiful death".</font>

369
00:37:33.042 --> 00:37:34.711
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I can only hope…</font>

370
00:37:34.878 --> 00:37:37.630
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…with all the world's warriors
gathered against us…</font>

371
00:37:37.797 --> 00:37:41.468
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…there might be one down there
who's up to the task.</font>

372
00:37:45.013 --> 00:37:46.222
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[LAUGHING]</font>

373
00:37:52.896 --> 00:37:54.772
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">PERSIAN EMISSARY:
Move!</font>

374
00:37:54.939 --> 00:37:55.982
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[WHIP CRACKING]</font>

375
00:37:56.524 --> 00:37:59.486
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Keep going, you dogs!</font>

376
00:38:07.160 --> 00:38:09.204
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Move!</font>

377
00:38:10.622 --> 00:38:13.208
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Forward, I say!</font>

378
00:38:15.543 --> 00:38:17.128
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Stop here!</font>

379
00:38:17.962 --> 00:38:20.131
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Who commands here?</font>

380
00:38:22.342 --> 00:38:25.011
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I am the emissary…</font>

381
00:38:25.178 --> 00:38:27.430
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…to the ruler of all the world…</font>

382
00:38:28.223 --> 00:38:32.143
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…the god of gods, king of kings…</font>

383
00:38:32.310 --> 00:38:33.895
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…and by that authority…</font>

384
00:38:34.062 --> 00:38:37.857
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…I demand that someone
show me your commander.</font>

385
00:38:41.611 --> 00:38:47.534
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Listen. Do you think the paltry dozen
you slew scares us?</font>

386
00:38:47.700 --> 00:38:51.204
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">These hills swarm with our scouts.</font>

387
00:38:51.371 --> 00:38:56.084
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">And do you think your pathetic wall
will do anything…</font>

388
00:38:56.251 --> 00:39:02.549
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…except fall like a heap of dry leaves
in the face of…?</font>

389
00:39:14.269 --> 00:39:16.563
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">STELIOS:
Our ancestors built this wall…</font>

390
00:39:17.272 --> 00:39:21.234
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…using ancient stones
from the bosom of Greece herself.</font>

391
00:39:21.651 --> 00:39:24.028
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">And with a little Spartan help…</font>

392
00:39:24.320 --> 00:39:26.781
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…your Persian scouts supplied the mortar.</font>

393
00:39:27.407 --> 00:39:31.369
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You will pay for your barbarism!</font>

394
00:39:50.513 --> 00:39:52.098
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">My arm!</font>

395
00:39:54.642 --> 00:39:56.519
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">STELIOS:
It's not yours anymore.</font>

396
00:39:56.811 --> 00:40:01.441
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Go now. Run along and tell your Xerxes
he faces free men here…</font>

397
00:40:01.816 --> 00:40:03.151
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…not slaves.</font>

398
00:40:03.318 --> 00:40:04.569
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Do it quickly…</font>

399
00:40:04.819 --> 00:40:07.739
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…before we decide to make our wall
just a little bit bigger.</font>

400
00:40:08.239 --> 00:40:09.824
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">No.</font>

401
00:40:09.991 --> 00:40:12.035
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Not slaves.</font>

402
00:40:12.201 --> 00:40:13.369
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[CHUCKLING]</font>

403
00:40:14.245 --> 00:40:17.665
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Your women will be slaves.</font>

404
00:40:17.999 --> 00:40:20.835
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Your sons, your daughters…</font>

405
00:40:21.002 --> 00:40:23.338
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…your elders will be slaves!</font>

406
00:40:23.504 --> 00:40:26.299
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">But not you, no.</font>

407
00:40:26.466 --> 00:40:30.511
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">By noon this day you will be dead men.</font>

408
00:40:31.679 --> 00:40:37.685
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">A thousand nations of the Persian Empire
descend upon you.</font>

409
00:40:38.102 --> 00:40:41.606
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Our arrows will blot out the sun.</font>

410
00:40:43.358 --> 00:40:46.069
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Then we will fight in the shade.</font>

411
00:40:47.612 --> 00:40:49.364
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">CAPTAIN:
The wall is solid.</font>

412
00:40:49.530 --> 00:40:52.700
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">It'll do the job of funneling the Persians
into the Hot Gates.</font>

413
00:40:53.034 --> 00:40:55.745
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Have the men found any route
through the hills to our back?</font>

414
00:40:56.245 --> 00:40:58.289
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">CAPTAIN:
None, sire.</font>

415
00:40:58.539 --> 00:41:00.124
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">There is such a route, good king.</font>

416
00:41:00.667 --> 00:41:02.377
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Just pass that western ridge.</font>

417
00:41:03.044 --> 00:41:04.754
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">It's an old goat path.</font>

418
00:41:04.921 --> 00:41:07.757
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">The Persians could use it to outflank us.</font>

419
00:41:07.924 --> 00:41:11.678
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Not one step closer, monster!</font>

420
00:41:13.304 --> 00:41:16.891
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Wise king, I humbly request an audience.</font>

421
00:41:17.058 --> 00:41:20.436
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">- I'll skewer you where you stand.
- I gave no such order.</font>

422
00:41:30.947 --> 00:41:32.198
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Forgive the captain.</font>

423
00:41:32.865 --> 00:41:34.367
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">He is a good soldier…</font>

424
00:41:34.909 --> 00:41:37.578
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…but a bit short on manners.</font>

425
00:41:37.745 --> 00:41:41.791
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">There is nothing to forgive, brave king.
I know what I look like.</font>

426
00:41:42.250 --> 00:41:44.252
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You wear the crimson of a Spartan.</font>

427
00:41:44.877 --> 00:41:50.508
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I am Ephialtes, born of Sparta.</font>

428
00:41:51.092 --> 00:41:55.179
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">My mother's love
led my parents to flee Sparta…</font>

429
00:41:55.346 --> 00:41:56.806
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…lest I be discarded.</font>

430
00:41:57.348 --> 00:42:00.143
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Your shield and armor?</font>

431
00:42:01.060 --> 00:42:02.729
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">My father's, sir.</font>

432
00:42:04.063 --> 00:42:08.109
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I beg you, bold king,
to permit me…</font>

433
00:42:08.276 --> 00:42:13.322
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…to redeem my father's name
by serving you in combat.</font>

434
00:42:13.614 --> 00:42:19.495
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">My father trained me to feel no fear,
to make spear and shield and sword…</font>

435
00:42:19.662 --> 00:42:22.415
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…as much a part of me
as my own beating heart.</font>

436
00:42:22.832 --> 00:42:26.127
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I will earn my father's armor, noble king…</font>

437
00:42:26.294 --> 00:42:28.463
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…by serving you in the battle.</font>

438
00:42:28.880 --> 00:42:30.298
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[GRUNTING]</font>

439
00:42:33.634 --> 00:42:35.762
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">A fine thrust.</font>

440
00:42:35.928 --> 00:42:37.513
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I will kill many Persians.</font>

441
00:42:43.394 --> 00:42:44.979
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Raise your shield.</font>

442
00:42:45.146 --> 00:42:47.815
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">- Sire?
- Raise your shield as high as you can.</font>

443
00:42:51.736 --> 00:42:53.070
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[GRUNTING]</font>

444
00:42:56.073 --> 00:42:59.118
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Your father should have taught you
how our phalanx works.</font>

445
00:42:59.786 --> 00:43:01.078
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">We fight…</font>

446
00:43:01.621 --> 00:43:04.499
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…as a single, impenetrable unit.</font>

447
00:43:04.665 --> 00:43:07.627
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">That is the source of our strength.</font>

448
00:43:08.461 --> 00:43:12.089
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Each Spartan protects the man
to his left…</font>

449
00:43:12.256 --> 00:43:15.468
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…from thigh to neck with his shield.</font>

450
00:43:15.635 --> 00:43:20.306
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">A single weak spot
and the phalanx shatters.</font>

451
00:43:21.682 --> 00:43:24.936
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">From thigh to neck, Ephialtes.</font>

452
00:43:26.979 --> 00:43:29.357
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I am sorry, my friend.</font>

453
00:43:29.524 --> 00:43:32.151
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">- But not all of us were made to be soldiers.
- But I…</font>

454
00:43:32.318 --> 00:43:34.737
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">- If you want to help in a Spartan victory…
- Yes.</font>

455
00:43:34.904 --> 00:43:40.076
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…clear the battlefield of the dead,
tend the wounded, bring them water…</font>

456
00:43:40.243 --> 00:43:41.869
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…but as for the fight itself…</font>

457
00:43:43.246 --> 00:43:45.164
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…I cannot use you.</font>

458
00:43:46.999 --> 00:43:48.417
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">EPHIALTES:
You…</font>

459
00:43:49.460 --> 00:43:51.295
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[CRIES]</font>

460
00:43:53.256 --> 00:43:54.549
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[GRUNTING]</font>

461
00:43:56.300 --> 00:44:00.388
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Mother! Father! You were wrong!</font>

462
00:44:03.683 --> 00:44:05.434
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You are wrong!</font>

463
00:44:05.601 --> 00:44:10.148
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Leonidas! You are wrong!</font>

464
00:44:10.606 --> 00:44:13.067
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Dispatch the Phocians to the goat path…</font>

465
00:44:13.234 --> 00:44:17.780
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…and pray to the gods
nobody tells the Persians about it.</font>

466
00:44:17.947 --> 00:44:19.240
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[RUMBLING]</font>

467
00:44:23.494 --> 00:44:25.079
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Earthquake.</font>

468
00:44:25.580 --> 00:44:26.831
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">LEONIDAS:
No, captain.</font>

469
00:44:28.416 --> 00:44:30.376
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Battle formations.</font>

470
00:44:46.601 --> 00:44:48.102
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[SHOUTING AND GRUNTING]</font>

471
00:44:54.275 --> 00:44:57.445
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">This is where we hold them.</font>

472
00:44:57.612 --> 00:44:59.906
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">This is where we fight!</font>

473
00:45:00.448 --> 00:45:02.700
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">This is where they die!</font>

474
00:45:03.034 --> 00:45:04.911
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Earn these shields, boys!</font>

475
00:45:05.411 --> 00:45:06.996
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[SPARTANS CHANT]</font>

476
00:45:07.622 --> 00:45:10.124
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Remember this day, men…</font>

477
00:45:10.291 --> 00:45:14.045
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…for it will be yours for all time.</font>

478
00:45:25.139 --> 00:45:26.933
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Spartans!</font>

479
00:45:27.099 --> 00:45:29.227
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Lay down your weapons!</font>

480
00:45:43.240 --> 00:45:44.492
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[HORSE NEIGHS]</font>

481
00:45:46.118 --> 00:45:48.371
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Persians!</font>

482
00:45:48.955 --> 00:45:50.998
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Come and get them!</font>

483
00:45:51.540 --> 00:45:52.667
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[HORN BLOWING]</font>

484
00:45:54.335 --> 00:45:55.378
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[PERSIANS SHOUTING]</font>

485
00:46:12.520 --> 00:46:14.146
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Hold!</font>

486
00:46:16.983 --> 00:46:18.526
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Give them nothing…</font>

487
00:46:18.985 --> 00:46:22.571
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…but take from them everything!</font>

488
00:46:24.281 --> 00:46:26.033
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Steady!</font>

489
00:46:27.868 --> 00:46:29.829
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[SHOUTING AND GRUNTING]</font>

490
00:46:36.794 --> 00:46:38.337
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Push!</font>

491
00:46:42.174 --> 00:46:44.552
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Is that the best you can do?</font>

492
00:46:46.762 --> 00:46:48.764
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Push! Push!</font>

493
00:46:51.642 --> 00:46:52.810
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[GRUNTING IN PAIN]</font>

494
00:46:58.858 --> 00:47:00.401
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Now!</font>

495
00:47:12.204 --> 00:47:13.706
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Push!</font>

496
00:47:57.249 --> 00:47:59.835
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">No prisoners!</font>

497
00:48:00.169 --> 00:48:01.921
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">No mercy!</font>

498
00:49:21.208 --> 00:49:23.377
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">They look thirsty.</font>

499
00:49:24.461 --> 00:49:27.381
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Well, let's give them something to drink.</font>

500
00:49:30.301 --> 00:49:32.970
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">To the cliffs.</font>

501
00:49:51.906 --> 00:49:53.240
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[SCREAMING]</font>

502
00:49:56.577 --> 00:49:58.746
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Halt.</font>

503
00:50:00.873 --> 00:50:02.958
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Hell of a good start.</font>

504
00:50:03.834 --> 00:50:05.294
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[CHANTING]</font>

505
00:50:25.606 --> 00:50:28.108
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Tuck tail!</font>

506
00:50:33.572 --> 00:50:35.115
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Persian cowards.</font>

507
00:50:39.036 --> 00:50:40.871
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[LAUGHING]</font>

508
00:50:42.915 --> 00:50:45.834
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">- What the hell are you laughing at?
- Well, you had to say it.</font>

509
00:50:46.627 --> 00:50:50.297
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">- What?
- "Fight in the shade".</font>

510
00:50:50.631 --> 00:50:51.924
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[LAUGHING]</font>

511
00:51:03.811 --> 00:51:05.771
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">LEONIDAS:
Recover.</font>

512
00:51:29.044 --> 00:51:31.672
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Today no Spartan dies.</font>

513
00:51:56.822 --> 00:51:58.240
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Easy, son.</font>

514
00:51:58.991 --> 00:52:00.200
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[HORSES NEIGHING]</font>

515
00:52:06.040 --> 00:52:07.291
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[GRUNTING]</font>

516
00:52:24.475 --> 00:52:26.435
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">DILIOS:
<i>We do what we were trained to do…</i></font>

517
00:52:26.602 --> 00:52:28.062
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…what we were bred to do…</i></font>

518
00:52:28.228 --> 00:52:31.231
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…what we were born to do.</i></font>

519
00:52:38.614 --> 00:52:41.617
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>No prisoners. No mercy.</i></font>

520
00:52:41.784 --> 00:52:43.243
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>A good start.</i></font>

521
00:53:52.730 --> 00:53:54.606
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">LOYALIST:
I was afraid you might not come.</font>

522
00:53:54.773 --> 00:53:55.983
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">GORGO:
I'm sorry, my son is…</font>

523
00:53:56.150 --> 00:54:01.780
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Is doing what children do best.
Please, don't apologize.</font>

524
00:54:02.781 --> 00:54:04.908
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Your son starts the <i>agoge</i> next year.</font>

525
00:54:05.492 --> 00:54:09.496
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">That is always a difficult time
for a Spartan mother.</font>

526
00:54:10.622 --> 00:54:15.169
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Yes, it will be hard. But also necessary.</font>

527
00:54:17.629 --> 00:54:21.842
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You will speak before the council
in two days' time.</font>

528
00:54:23.719 --> 00:54:25.763
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">My husband does not have two days.</font>

529
00:54:26.180 --> 00:54:28.140
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Think of the two days as a gift.</font>

530
00:54:30.184 --> 00:54:32.227
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">It's no secret…</font>

531
00:54:32.394 --> 00:54:35.272
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…Theron wants what you control.</font>

532
00:54:35.439 --> 00:54:38.275
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">It's his voice you must silence.</font>

533
00:54:38.442 --> 00:54:40.527
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Make him your ally…</font>

534
00:54:40.861 --> 00:54:43.405
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…and you will have your victory.</font>

535
00:54:44.198 --> 00:54:45.991
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Thank you.</font>

536
00:54:46.325 --> 00:54:48.702
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You are wise as you are kind.</font>

537
00:55:15.521 --> 00:55:17.564
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">THERON:
Ah, there's your mother.</font>

538
00:55:24.029 --> 00:55:27.449
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You should keep a better eye on him
if he's to be king one day.</font>

539
00:55:27.658 --> 00:55:30.118
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Be unfortunate if anything
were to happen to him.</font>

540
00:55:31.620 --> 00:55:33.497
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Or to his beautiful mother.</font>

541
00:55:49.555 --> 00:55:51.056
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">PERSIAN:
No! Ann!</font>

542
00:55:54.268 --> 00:55:59.731
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Our Greek comrades are begging
for a crack at the Persians, sire.</font>

543
00:56:00.023 --> 00:56:01.358
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Good.</font>

544
00:56:01.525 --> 00:56:04.278
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I've got something
I think they can handle.</font>

545
00:56:04.778 --> 00:56:06.488
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Tell Daxos that I want him…</font>

546
00:56:06.655 --> 00:56:11.201
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…and 20 of his best eager, sober
and ready for the next charge.</font>

547
00:56:11.368 --> 00:56:13.203
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">King Leonidas.</font>

548
00:56:15.706 --> 00:56:19.501
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">- Stelios, catch your breath, boy.
- Yes, milord.</font>

549
00:56:20.127 --> 00:56:22.296
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">The Persians are approaching.</font>

550
00:56:23.630 --> 00:56:27.509
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">A small contingent.
Too small for an attack.</font>

551
00:56:31.263 --> 00:56:34.808
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">LEONIDAS: Captain, I leave you in charge.
CAPTAIN: But sire…</font>

552
00:56:34.975 --> 00:56:36.226
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">LEONIDAS:
Relax, old friend.</font>

553
00:56:36.393 --> 00:56:40.981
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">If they assassinate me,
all of Sparta goes to war.</font>

554
00:56:41.898 --> 00:56:44.484
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Pray they're that stupid.</font>

555
00:56:45.611 --> 00:56:47.321
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Pray…</font>

556
00:56:47.821 --> 00:56:50.032
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…we're that lucky.</font>

557
00:56:53.160 --> 00:56:54.953
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Besides…</font>

558
00:56:57.205 --> 00:57:00.542
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…there's no reason we can't be civil…</font>

559
00:57:00.834 --> 00:57:02.461
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…is there?</font>

560
00:57:02.878 --> 00:57:03.879
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[PERSIAN GRUNTS IN PAIN]</font>

561
00:57:04.046 --> 00:57:05.547
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">None, sire.</font>

562
00:57:24.191 --> 00:57:26.401
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Let me guess.</font>

563
00:57:27.152 --> 00:57:30.155
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You must be Xerxes.</font>

564
00:57:42.167 --> 00:57:44.378
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Come, Leonidas.</font>

565
00:57:45.796 --> 00:57:47.547
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Let us reason together.</font>

566
00:57:47.839 --> 00:57:49.800
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">It would be a regrettable waste…</font>

567
00:57:50.217 --> 00:57:53.387
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…it would be nothing short of madness
were you, brave king…</font>

568
00:57:53.553 --> 00:57:56.765
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…and your valiant troops to perish…</font>

569
00:57:57.391 --> 00:57:59.476
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…all because of a simple
misunderstanding.</font>

570
00:58:00.060 --> 00:58:02.896
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">- There's much our cultures could share.
- Haven't you noticed?</font>

571
00:58:03.063 --> 00:58:05.482
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">We've been sharing our culture
with you all morning.</font>

572
00:58:06.066 --> 00:58:08.360
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Yours is a fascinating tribe.</font>

573
00:58:08.527 --> 00:58:10.696
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Even now you are defiant…</font>

574
00:58:10.862 --> 00:58:14.992
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…in the face of annihilation
and the presence of a god.</font>

575
00:58:15.158 --> 00:58:17.202
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">It isn't wise to stand against me,
Leonidas.</font>

576
00:58:17.869 --> 00:58:20.080
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Imagine what a horrible fate
awaits my enemies…</font>

577
00:58:20.247 --> 00:58:23.166
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…when I would gladly kill
any of my own men for victory.</font>

578
00:58:23.333 --> 00:58:25.961
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">And I would die for any one of mine.</font>

579
00:58:26.128 --> 00:58:30.382
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You Greeks take pride in your logic.
I suggest you employ it.</font>

580
00:58:30.549 --> 00:58:34.094
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Consider the beautiful land
you so vigorously defend.</font>

581
00:58:34.261 --> 00:58:36.763
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Picture it reduced to ash at my whim.</font>

582
00:58:37.013 --> 00:58:38.473
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Consider the fate of your women.</font>

583
00:58:39.099 --> 00:58:41.601
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Clearly you don't know our women.</font>

584
00:58:41.768 --> 00:58:45.313
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I might as well have marched them up here,
judging by what I've seen.</font>

585
00:58:46.440 --> 00:58:48.942
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You have many slaves, Xerxes…</font>

586
00:58:49.901 --> 00:58:52.195
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…but few warriors.</font>

587
00:58:52.362 --> 00:58:56.283
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">It won't be long
before they fear my spears…</font>

588
00:58:56.700 --> 00:58:59.119
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…more than your whips.</font>

589
00:59:02.956 --> 00:59:05.834
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">It's not the lash they fear…</font>

590
00:59:08.587 --> 00:59:10.255
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…it is my divine power.</font>

591
00:59:10.964 --> 00:59:15.469
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">But I am a generous god.
I can make you rich beyond all measure.</font>

592
00:59:15.927 --> 00:59:18.305
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I will make you warlord of all Greece.</font>

593
00:59:18.972 --> 00:59:22.851
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You will carry my battle standard
to the heart of Europa.</font>

594
00:59:23.018 --> 00:59:25.645
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Your Athenian rivals…</font>

595
00:59:25.937 --> 00:59:28.106
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…will kneel at your feet…</font>

596
00:59:28.815 --> 00:59:31.610
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…if you will but kneel at mine.</font>

597
00:59:32.444 --> 00:59:34.696
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You are generous…</font>

598
00:59:35.280 --> 00:59:37.657
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…as you are divine…</font>

599
00:59:38.408 --> 00:59:40.035
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…O king of kings.</font>

600
00:59:40.202 --> 00:59:44.122
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Such an offer
only a madman would refuse.</font>

601
00:59:44.706 --> 00:59:46.708
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">But the…</font>

602
00:59:47.626 --> 00:59:50.462
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">The idea of kneeling, it's…</font>

603
00:59:50.629 --> 00:59:55.175
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You see, slaughtering
all those men of yours has…</font>

604
00:59:55.342 --> 00:59:59.179
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Well, it's left a nasty cramp in my leg…</font>

605
00:59:59.346 --> 01:00:01.431
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…so kneeling will be hard for me.</font>

606
01:00:01.681 --> 01:00:05.060
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">There will be no glory in your sacrifice.</font>

607
01:00:05.227 --> 01:00:08.855
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I will erase even the memory of Sparta
from the histories.</font>

608
01:00:09.022 --> 01:00:12.192
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Every piece of Greek parchment
shall be burned.</font>

609
01:00:12.359 --> 01:00:15.695
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Every Greek historian and every scribe
shall have their eyes put out…</font>

610
01:00:15.862 --> 01:00:18.156
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…and their tongues
cut from their mouths.</font>

611
01:00:18.323 --> 01:00:24.329
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Why, uttering the very name of Sparta
or Leonidas will be punishable by death.</font>

612
01:00:24.955 --> 01:00:28.208
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">The world will never know
you existed at all.</font>

613
01:00:30.377 --> 01:00:34.965
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">The world will know
that free men stood against a tyrant.</font>

614
01:00:35.173 --> 01:00:38.677
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">That few stood against many.</font>

615
01:00:39.052 --> 01:00:42.222
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">And before this battle was over…</font>

616
01:00:42.472 --> 01:00:45.433
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…that even a god-king can bleed.</font>

617
01:00:52.816 --> 01:00:55.026
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You fought well today…</font>

618
01:00:56.361 --> 01:00:58.238
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…for a woman.</font>

619
01:00:59.406 --> 01:01:01.074
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">As did you.</font>

620
01:01:01.241 --> 01:01:04.369
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Maybe if I'm injured,
you'll be able to keep up with me.</font>

621
01:01:04.870 --> 01:01:09.833
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">STELIOS: Perhaps I was so
far ahead you couldn't see me.</font>

622
01:01:10.417 --> 01:01:13.628
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">More likely offering your backside
to the Thespians.</font>

623
01:01:14.588 --> 01:01:16.214
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Jealousy…</font>

624
01:01:16.381 --> 01:01:18.884
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…does not become you, my friend.</font>

625
01:01:21.595 --> 01:01:23.930
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Move it, men!</font>

626
01:01:26.057 --> 01:01:28.268
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Pile those Persians high.</font>

627
01:01:31.438 --> 01:01:34.232
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">For unless I miss my guess…</font>

628
01:01:34.774 --> 01:01:37.777
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…we're in for one wild night.</font>

629
01:01:56.630 --> 01:01:58.298
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[BIRD CRYING]</font>

630
01:02:01.718 --> 01:02:06.890
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">DILIOS: <i>They have served the dark
will of Persian kings for 500 years.</i></font>

631
01:02:07.057 --> 01:02:09.392
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Eyes as dark as night.</i></font>

632
01:02:09.559 --> 01:02:11.561
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Teeth filed to fangs.</i></font>

633
01:02:13.647 --> 01:02:15.941
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Soulless.</i></font>

634
01:02:23.323 --> 01:02:28.119
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>The personal guard to King Xerxes himself.
The Persian warrior elite.</i></font>

635
01:02:29.913 --> 01:02:32.999
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>The deadliest fighting force in all of Asia:</i></font>

636
01:02:33.792 --> 01:02:35.835
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>The Immortals.</i></font>

637
01:02:44.052 --> 01:02:47.472
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>The god-king has betrayed a fatal flaw:</i></font>

638
01:02:47.973 --> 01:02:49.724
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Hubris.</i></font>

639
01:02:51.977 --> 01:02:54.729
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Easy to taunt, easy to trick.</i></font>

640
01:02:55.397 --> 01:02:57.857
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Before wounds and weariness
have taken their toll…</i></font>

641
01:02:58.024 --> 01:03:01.528
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…the mad king
throws the best he has at us.</i></font>

642
01:03:02.028 --> 01:03:03.738
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Xerxes has taken the bait.</i></font>

643
01:03:03.905 --> 01:03:05.699
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Spartans, push!</font>

644
01:03:06.700 --> 01:03:08.410
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[GRUNTING]</font>

645
01:03:16.376 --> 01:03:18.003
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">DILIOS:
<i>Immortals.</i></font>

646
01:03:18.461 --> 01:03:21.423
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>We put their name to the test.</i></font>

647
01:03:23.008 --> 01:03:24.426
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[GRUNTING]</font>

648
01:03:48.033 --> 01:03:49.701
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[IMMORTAL GROWLING]</font>

649
01:04:05.592 --> 01:04:07.052
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">STELIOS:
Father!</font>

650
01:04:16.186 --> 01:04:17.604
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[IMMORTAL GROWLING]</font>

651
01:05:39.978 --> 01:05:41.437
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[SNARLING]</font>

652
01:05:52.699 --> 01:05:53.992
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">SPARTAN:
My king!</font>

653
01:06:37.327 --> 01:06:38.870
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[SNARLING]</font>

654
01:06:51.424 --> 01:06:52.926
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[GRUNTING]</font>

655
01:07:06.773 --> 01:07:08.733
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Arcadians, now!</font>

656
01:07:11.027 --> 01:07:13.780
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Go! Show the Spartans what we can do.</font>

657
01:07:14.405 --> 01:07:15.823
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Go!</font>

658
01:07:15.990 --> 01:07:17.283
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">[ARCADIANS SHOUTING
AND GRUNTING]</font>

659
01:07:25.250 --> 01:07:27.126
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">DILIOS:
<i>They shout and curse…</i></font>

660
01:07:27.293 --> 01:07:30.505
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…stabbing wildly,
more brawlers than warriors.</i></font>

661
01:07:31.631 --> 01:07:34.217
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>They make a wondrous mess of things.</i></font>

662
01:07:35.260 --> 01:07:38.012
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Brave amateurs, they do their part.</i></font>

663
01:08:25.643 --> 01:08:27.520
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Immortals.</i></font>

664
01:08:27.687 --> 01:08:30.273
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>They fail our king's test.</i></font>

665
01:08:30.440 --> 01:08:33.359
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>And a man who fancies himself a god…</i></font>

666
01:08:34.110 --> 01:08:39.032
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…feels a very human chill
crawl up his spine.</i></font>

667
01:08:46.164 --> 01:08:48.291
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">To our king!</font>

668
01:08:48.666 --> 01:08:50.668
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">And our honored dead.</font>

669
01:08:50.835 --> 01:08:53.629
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Whom will Xerxes dare to send next?
Whom?!</font>

670
01:08:53.963 --> 01:08:56.674
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">There's nothing that can stop us now!</font>

671
01:08:57.550 --> 01:09:01.054
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Even the king allows himself
to hope for more than glory.</i></font>

672
01:09:01.220 --> 01:09:04.557
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Such mad hope, but there it is:</i></font>

673
01:09:05.016 --> 01:09:10.396
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>"Against Asia's endless hordes,
against all odds, we can do it.</i></font>

674
01:09:10.563 --> 01:09:13.316
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>We can hold the Hot Gates.</i></font>

675
01:09:13.483 --> 01:09:15.610
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>We can win".</i></font>

676
01:09:23.201 --> 01:09:24.952
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Dawn.</i></font>

677
01:09:25.578 --> 01:09:29.582
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Whips crack. Barbarians howl.</i></font>

678
01:09:29.749 --> 01:09:33.670
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Those behind cry, "Forward!"</i></font>

679
01:09:35.546 --> 01:09:39.342
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Those in front cry, "Back!"</i></font>

680
01:09:45.431 --> 01:09:47.975
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Our eyes bear witness
to the grotesque spectacle…</i></font>

681
01:09:48.142 --> 01:09:52.271
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…coughed forth from the darkest corner
of Xerxes' empire.</i></font>

682
01:10:42.488 --> 01:10:43.990
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>When muscle failed…</i></font>

683
01:10:44.449 --> 01:10:47.118
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…they turned to their magic.</i></font>

684
01:10:48.161 --> 01:10:52.957
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>One hundred nations descend upon us,
the armies of all Asia.</i></font>

685
01:10:53.124 --> 01:10:57.587
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Funneled into this narrow corridor,
their numbers count for nothing.</i></font>

686
01:11:31.954 --> 01:11:33.915
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>They fall by the hundreds.</i></font>

687
01:11:34.081 --> 01:11:39.712
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>We send the severed bodies
and the fragile hearts back to Xerxes' feet.</i></font>

688
01:11:56.312 --> 01:12:00.483
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>King Xerxes is displeased
with his generals.</i></font>

689
01:12:00.650 --> 01:12:03.236
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>He disciplines them.</i></font>

690
01:12:20.086 --> 01:12:24.507
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Xerxes dispatches his monsters
from half the world away.</i></font>

691
01:12:35.476 --> 01:12:37.603
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>They're clumsy beasts…</i></font>

692
01:12:37.770 --> 01:12:40.106
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…and the piled Persian dead are slippery.</i></font>

693
01:13:16.559 --> 01:13:18.978
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">- You still here?
- Somebody's gotta watch your back.</font>

694
01:13:19.145 --> 01:13:20.771
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Not now, I'm a little busy.</font>

695
01:14:01.020 --> 01:14:03.564
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Regroup!</font>

696
01:14:06.776 --> 01:14:08.402
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Astinos!</font>

697
01:14:08.611 --> 01:14:10.321
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">My son!</font>

698
01:14:19.246 --> 01:14:20.873
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Astinos!</font>

699
01:14:21.040 --> 01:14:23.834
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">No!</font>

700
01:14:47.066 --> 01:14:49.235
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Day wears on.</i></font>

701
01:14:49.568 --> 01:14:51.737
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>We lose few…</i></font>

702
01:14:51.904 --> 01:14:55.116
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…but each felled is a friend,
or dearest blood.</i></font>

703
01:14:57.326 --> 01:15:01.247
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>And upon seeing the headless body
of his own young son…</i></font>

704
01:15:01.414 --> 01:15:03.249
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…the captain breaks rank.</i></font>

705
01:15:03.416 --> 01:15:06.877
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>He goes wild, blood-drunk.</i></font>

706
01:15:31.485 --> 01:15:33.988
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>The captain's cries of pain
at the loss of his son…</i></font>

707
01:15:34.155 --> 01:15:37.908
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…are more frightening to the enemy
than the deepest battle drums.</i></font>

708
01:15:38.075 --> 01:15:42.079
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>It takes three men to restrain him
and bring him back to our own.</i></font>

709
01:15:42.413 --> 01:15:44.749
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>The day is ours.</i></font>

710
01:15:45.124 --> 01:15:47.793
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>No songs are sung.</i></font>

711
01:16:27.917 --> 01:16:32.505
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Your gods were cruel to shape you so,
friend Ephialtes.</font>

712
01:16:34.924 --> 01:16:36.217
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">The Spartans, too…</font>

713
01:16:36.967 --> 01:16:39.845
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…were cruel to reject you.</font>

714
01:16:42.681 --> 01:16:45.142
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">But I am kind.</font>

715
01:16:51.649 --> 01:16:53.776
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Everything you could ever desire…</font>

716
01:16:55.027 --> 01:16:56.779
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…every happiness you can imagine…</font>

717
01:16:58.989 --> 01:17:03.577
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…every pleasure your fellow Greeks
and your false gods have denied you…</font>

718
01:17:04.370 --> 01:17:06.664
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…I will grant you.</font>

719
01:17:07.915 --> 01:17:10.334
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">For I am kind.</font>

720
01:17:24.265 --> 01:17:27.560
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Embrace me as your king
and as your god.</font>

721
01:17:28.727 --> 01:17:30.396
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Yes.</font>

722
01:17:31.897 --> 01:17:36.694
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Lead my soldiers to the hidden path
that empties behind the cursed Spartans…</font>

723
01:17:36.861 --> 01:17:39.113
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…and your joys will be endless.</font>

724
01:17:47.580 --> 01:17:50.749
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Yes! I want it all.</font>

725
01:17:51.166 --> 01:17:54.753
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Wealth. Women.</font>

726
01:17:56.755 --> 01:17:58.424
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">And one more thing…</font>

727
01:18:01.594 --> 01:18:04.263
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…I want a uniform.</font>

728
01:18:08.767 --> 01:18:10.477
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Done.</font>

729
01:18:12.104 --> 01:18:13.814
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You will find…</font>

730
01:18:14.440 --> 01:18:16.358
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…I am kind.</font>

731
01:18:17.484 --> 01:18:21.739
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Unlike the cruel Leonidas,
who demanded that you stand…</font>

732
01:18:23.824 --> 01:18:25.534
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…I require only…</font>

733
01:18:26.285 --> 01:18:27.703
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…that you kneel.</font>

734
01:18:55.356 --> 01:18:57.316
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Beautiful night.</font>

735
01:18:58.734 --> 01:19:02.738
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Yes, but I did not ask you here
for small talk, Theron.</font>

736
01:19:03.364 --> 01:19:05.491
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You can be sure of that.</font>

737
01:19:06.867 --> 01:19:09.536
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You never spared words with me.</font>

738
01:19:10.120 --> 01:19:13.374
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Can I offer you something?
A drink, perhaps?</font>

739
01:19:13.540 --> 01:19:15.376
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Is it poison?</font>

740
01:19:15.793 --> 01:19:18.545
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I'm sorry to disappoint you,
it's only water.</font>

741
01:19:28.347 --> 01:19:31.517
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I'm told it's been arranged for you
to go before the council.</font>

742
01:19:32.184 --> 01:19:33.894
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Yes.</font>

743
01:19:34.103 --> 01:19:37.439
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I need your help in winning votes
to send the army north to our king.</font>

744
01:19:38.023 --> 01:19:39.650
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Yes.</font>

745
01:19:40.317 --> 01:19:42.861
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I can see it,
the two of us standing together.</font>

746
01:19:43.028 --> 01:19:47.408
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Me, politician. You, warrior.
Our voices as one.</font>

747
01:19:48.742 --> 01:19:50.202
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">But why would I want to do that?</font>

748
01:19:51.203 --> 01:19:55.165
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">It proves you care for a king who right now
fights for the very water we drink.</font>

749
01:19:55.499 --> 01:19:57.084
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">True.</font>

750
01:19:57.459 --> 01:20:00.087
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">But this is politics, not war.</font>

751
01:20:00.379 --> 01:20:01.922
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Leonidas is an idealist.</font>

752
01:20:02.339 --> 01:20:06.260
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I know your kind too well. You send men
to slaughter for your own gain.</font>

753
01:20:06.427 --> 01:20:11.348
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Your husband, our king,
has taken 300 of our finest to slaughter.</font>

754
01:20:11.515 --> 01:20:16.145
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">He's broken our laws
and left without the council's consent.</font>

755
01:20:16.645 --> 01:20:19.648
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">- I'm simply a realist.
- You're an opportunist.</font>

756
01:20:20.607 --> 01:20:24.903
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You're as foolish as Leonidas if you think
men don't have a price in this world.</font>

757
01:20:25.070 --> 01:20:29.658
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">All men are not created equal.
That's the Spartan code, my little queen.</font>

758
01:20:33.328 --> 01:20:35.748
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I admire your passion.</font>

759
01:20:37.082 --> 01:20:38.792
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">But don't think that you…</font>

760
01:20:39.251 --> 01:20:41.587
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…a woman, even a queen…</font>

761
01:20:41.754 --> 01:20:45.674
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…can walk into the council chamber
and sway the minds of men.</font>

762
01:20:45.841 --> 01:20:48.260
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I own that chamber…</font>

763
01:20:48.427 --> 01:20:50.512
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…as if it were built with these hands.</font>

764
01:20:54.975 --> 01:20:58.520
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I could crush
the life out of you right now.</font>

765
01:20:59.605 --> 01:21:03.275
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You will go before the council,
but your words will fall on deaf ears.</font>

766
01:21:03.442 --> 01:21:09.198
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Leonidas will receive no reinforcements,
and if he returns, without my help…</font>

767
01:21:09.364 --> 01:21:12.326
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…he will go to jail or worse.</font>

768
01:21:16.080 --> 01:21:17.539
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Do you love your Sparta?</font>

769
01:21:18.040 --> 01:21:19.750
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Yes.</font>

770
01:21:19.917 --> 01:21:22.169
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">- And your king?
- I do.</font>

771
01:21:28.008 --> 01:21:31.720
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Your husband fights for his land
and his love.</font>

772
01:21:32.388 --> 01:21:34.681
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">What do you have to offer…</font>

773
01:21:35.474 --> 01:21:38.435
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…in return for my word
that I'll help you send our army north?</font>

774
01:21:42.398 --> 01:21:45.067
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">What does a realist want with his queen?</font>

775
01:21:49.655 --> 01:21:51.406
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I think you know.</font>

776
01:22:05.838 --> 01:22:08.549
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">This will not be over quickly.</font>

777
01:22:09.591 --> 01:22:12.094
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You will not enjoy this.</font>

778
01:22:12.636 --> 01:22:14.888
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I'm not your king.</font>

779
01:22:39.705 --> 01:22:41.498
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Dilios.</font>

780
01:22:43.500 --> 01:22:47.546
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I trust that scratch
hasn't made you useless?</font>

781
01:22:47.713 --> 01:22:50.716
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Hardly, my lord. It's just an eye.</font>

782
01:22:50.883 --> 01:22:54.094
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">The gods saw fit to grace me
with a spare.</font>

783
01:22:55.971 --> 01:22:57.890
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">My captain?</font>

784
01:22:59.224 --> 01:23:03.020
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Curses the gods and mourns alone.</font>

785
01:23:04.980 --> 01:23:06.940
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Leonidas!</font>

786
01:23:08.150 --> 01:23:11.153
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">We are undone.
Undone, I tell you. Destroyed.</font>

787
01:23:11.320 --> 01:23:12.738
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Daxos, calm yourself.</font>

788
01:23:12.905 --> 01:23:16.533
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Our hunchback traitor led Xerxes' Immortals
to the hidden goat path behind us.</font>

789
01:23:16.909 --> 01:23:19.745
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">The Phocians you posted there
were scattered without a fight.</font>

790
01:23:19.912 --> 01:23:25.167
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">- This battle is over, Leonidas.
- This battle is over when I say it is over.</font>

791
01:23:25.334 --> 01:23:29.713
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">By morning, the Immortals will surround us.
The Hot Gates will fall.</font>

792
01:23:30.339 --> 01:23:34.718
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Spartans! Prepare for glory!</font>

793
01:23:34.885 --> 01:23:38.096
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Glory? Have you gone mad?</font>

794
01:23:38.263 --> 01:23:39.806
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">There is no glory to be had now.</font>

795
01:23:40.432 --> 01:23:44.019
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Only retreat or surrender. Or death.</font>

796
01:23:44.186 --> 01:23:47.356
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Well, that's an easy choice
for us, Arcadian.</font>

797
01:23:47.522 --> 01:23:53.028
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Spartans never retreat.
Spartans never surrender.</font>

798
01:23:53.612 --> 01:23:55.739
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Go spread the word.</font>

799
01:23:55.948 --> 01:23:59.618
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Let every Greek assembled
know the truth of this.</font>

800
01:23:59.785 --> 01:24:02.621
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Let each among them
search his own soul.</font>

801
01:24:04.331 --> 01:24:08.460
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">And while you're at it, search your own.</font>

802
01:24:15.968 --> 01:24:18.262
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">My men will leave with me.</font>

803
01:24:23.600 --> 01:24:25.811
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Godspeed, Leonidas.</font>

804
01:24:32.150 --> 01:24:33.735
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Children!</font>

805
01:24:34.695 --> 01:24:36.029
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Children.</font>

806
01:24:37.072 --> 01:24:39.074
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Gather round.</font>

807
01:24:40.951 --> 01:24:44.204
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">No retreat, no surrender.</font>

808
01:24:44.371 --> 01:24:48.250
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">That is Spartan law.</font>

809
01:24:48.500 --> 01:24:53.547
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">And by Spartan law,
we will stand and fight…</font>

810
01:24:53.714 --> 01:24:55.716
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…and die.</font>

811
01:24:59.177 --> 01:25:02.681
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">A new age has begun.</font>

812
01:25:04.391 --> 01:25:07.519
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">An age of freedom.</font>

813
01:25:08.603 --> 01:25:12.274
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">And all will know that 300 Spartans…</font>

814
01:25:12.441 --> 01:25:15.694
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…gave their last breath to defend it.</font>

815
01:25:36.006 --> 01:25:37.758
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">My friend.</font>

816
01:25:41.303 --> 01:25:46.892
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I have lived my entire life
without regret until now.</font>

817
01:25:50.228 --> 01:25:56.193
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">It's not that my son
gave up his life for his country.</font>

818
01:25:58.070 --> 01:26:01.948
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">It's just that I never told him
that I loved him the most.</font>

819
01:26:03.575 --> 01:26:06.411
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">That he stood by me with honor.</font>

820
01:26:07.871 --> 01:26:10.791
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">That he was all that was best in me.</font>

821
01:26:19.925 --> 01:26:22.427
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">My heart is broken for your loss.</font>

822
01:26:23.178 --> 01:26:24.888
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Heart?</font>

823
01:26:29.935 --> 01:26:33.063
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I have filled my heart…</font>

824
01:26:33.230 --> 01:26:34.940
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…with hate.</font>

825
01:26:39.111 --> 01:26:40.779
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Good.</font>

826
01:26:49.913 --> 01:26:51.748
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Dilios…</font>

827
01:26:53.458 --> 01:26:55.585
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…let's take a walk.</font>

828
01:26:57.045 --> 01:26:59.131
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Yes, my lord.</font>

829
01:27:01.508 --> 01:27:04.177
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">But, sire, I am fit and ready for battle.</font>

830
01:27:04.344 --> 01:27:07.472
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">That you are, one of the finest.</font>

831
01:27:07.806 --> 01:27:11.393
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">But you have another talent
unlike any other Spartan.</font>

832
01:27:14.104 --> 01:27:17.524
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You will deliver my final orders
to the council…</font>

833
01:27:17.691 --> 01:27:20.193
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…with force and verve.</font>

834
01:27:22.696 --> 01:27:24.990
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Tell them our story.</font>

835
01:27:25.157 --> 01:27:29.661
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Make every Greek know
what happened here.</font>

836
01:27:30.495 --> 01:27:33.165
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You'll have a grand tale to tell.</font>

837
01:27:34.958 --> 01:27:36.668
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">A tale of victory.</font>

838
01:27:37.335 --> 01:27:38.879
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Victory.</font>

839
01:27:42.924 --> 01:27:44.926
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Yes, my lord.</font>

840
01:27:50.599 --> 01:27:52.976
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Sire, any message…?</font>

841
01:27:55.854 --> 01:27:57.189
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">For the queen?</font>

842
01:28:19.669 --> 01:28:22.088
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">None that need be spoken.</font>

843
01:28:37.229 --> 01:28:39.606
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Hundreds leave.</i></font>

844
01:28:40.232 --> 01:28:42.692
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>A handful stay.</i></font>

845
01:28:47.864 --> 01:28:50.492
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Only one looks back.</i></font>

846
01:29:00.794 --> 01:29:03.004
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Spartans!</font>

847
01:29:04.089 --> 01:29:07.259
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Ready your breakfast and eat hearty…</font>

848
01:29:07.425 --> 01:29:11.346
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…for tonight we dine in hell!</font>

849
01:29:20.230 --> 01:29:22.899
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">May I give the floor now…</font>

850
01:29:23.066 --> 01:29:27.487
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…to the wife of Leonidas
and queen of Sparta.</font>

851
01:29:39.207 --> 01:29:40.959
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">- What's this?
- This is nothing.</font>

852
01:29:41.126 --> 01:29:42.961
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Councilmen…</font>

853
01:29:43.128 --> 01:29:46.881
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…I stand before you
not only as your queen.</font>

854
01:29:47.757 --> 01:29:50.468
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I come to you as a mother.</font>

855
01:29:51.761 --> 01:29:54.139
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I come to you as a wife.</font>

856
01:29:55.974 --> 01:29:58.476
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I come to you as a Spartan woman.</font>

857
01:30:03.481 --> 01:30:06.610
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I come to you with great humility.</font>

858
01:30:10.030 --> 01:30:12.449
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I am not here to represent Leonidas.</font>

859
01:30:12.616 --> 01:30:15.368
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">His actions speak louder
than my words ever could.</font>

860
01:30:15.702 --> 01:30:18.121
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I am here for all those voices
which cannot be heard.</font>

861
01:30:18.288 --> 01:30:20.832
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Mothers, daughters, fathers, sons.</font>

862
01:30:20.999 --> 01:30:23.960
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Three hundred families
that bleed for our rights…</font>

863
01:30:24.377 --> 01:30:27.589
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…and for the very principles
this room was built upon.</font>

864
01:30:28.173 --> 01:30:30.300
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">We are at war, gentlemen.</font>

865
01:30:30.717 --> 01:30:33.261
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">We must send the entire Spartan army
to aid our king…</font>

866
01:30:33.428 --> 01:30:36.514
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…in the preservation of not just ourselves,
but of our children.</font>

867
01:30:37.098 --> 01:30:40.226
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Send the army
for the preservation of liberty.</font>

868
01:30:40.393 --> 01:30:42.729
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Send it for justice.</font>

869
01:30:42.896 --> 01:30:44.522
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Send it for law and order.</font>

870
01:30:45.065 --> 01:30:47.275
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Send it for reason.</font>

871
01:30:47.442 --> 01:30:51.529
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">But most importantly,
send our army for hope.</font>

872
01:30:51.696 --> 01:30:55.283
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Hope that a king and his men have not
been wasted to the pages of history.</font>

873
01:30:56.117 --> 01:30:59.537
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">That their courage bonds us together.</font>

874
01:30:59.871 --> 01:31:03.041
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">That we are made stronger
by their actions…</font>

875
01:31:04.042 --> 01:31:08.171
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…and that your choices today
reflect their bravery.</font>

876
01:31:10.090 --> 01:31:11.758
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Three hundred.</font>

877
01:31:14.094 --> 01:31:15.929
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">We must send them.</font>

878
01:31:19.724 --> 01:31:21.559
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Moving…</font>

879
01:31:21.893 --> 01:31:24.771
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…eloquent, passionate.</font>

880
01:31:25.188 --> 01:31:29.359
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">But it doesn't change the fact
that your husband has brought war upon us.</font>

881
01:31:29.526 --> 01:31:31.945
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You are wrong.
Xerxes brought it forth…</font>

882
01:31:32.112 --> 01:31:34.572
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…and before that,
his father Darius at Marathon.</font>

883
01:31:34.739 --> 01:31:36.491
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">The Persians will not stop…</font>

884
01:31:36.658 --> 01:31:40.036
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…until the only shelter we will find
is rubble and chaos.</font>

885
01:31:40.412 --> 01:31:44.165
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">This chamber needs no
history lesson, my queen.</font>

886
01:31:44.666 --> 01:31:46.876
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Then what is the lesson
you would like to leave?</font>

887
01:31:47.043 --> 01:31:49.129
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Shall I begin to enumerate all of them?</font>

888
01:31:49.546 --> 01:31:52.966
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Honor. Duty. Glory.</font>

889
01:31:53.258 --> 01:31:58.263
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You speak of honor, duty and glory?</font>

890
01:31:59.597 --> 01:32:00.807
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">But what of adultery?</font>

891
01:32:00.974 --> 01:32:03.435
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">- How dare you.
- How dare I?</font>

892
01:32:03.893 --> 01:32:06.896
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Watch her carefully.</font>

893
01:32:07.063 --> 01:32:10.024
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">She is a trickster in true form.</font>

894
01:32:10.191 --> 01:32:13.361
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Do not play with the members
of this sacred chamber, my queen.</font>

895
01:32:13.528 --> 01:32:16.614
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Just hours ago,
you offered yourself to me.</font>

896
01:32:16.781 --> 01:32:21.244
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Were I a weaker man,
I would have her scent on me still.</font>

897
01:32:21.411 --> 01:32:24.414
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">- This is outrage.
- Oh, the hypocrite speaks!</font>

898
01:32:24.581 --> 01:32:27.584
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Did you not receive a similar payment,
which you took…</font>

899
01:32:27.751 --> 01:32:30.962
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…in exchange for her having an audience
with these noble men?</font>

900
01:32:31.129 --> 01:32:32.922
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">- That is a lie.
- Is it?</font>

901
01:32:33.089 --> 01:32:36.843
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Was he not, by your invitation,
asked to come to the king's bedchamber?</font>

902
01:32:37.385 --> 01:32:42.015
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">The very bed where you attempted
to negotiate with me so vigorously?</font>

903
01:32:44.642 --> 01:32:48.146
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You look shocked.
A bribe of the flesh, gentlemen…</font>

904
01:32:48.313 --> 01:32:51.608
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…while her husband
promotes anarchy and war.</font>

905
01:32:54.527 --> 01:32:55.737
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">He speaks truth.</font>

906
01:32:56.321 --> 01:32:59.532
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Words escape
even the most cunning tongue…</font>

907
01:32:59.699 --> 01:33:01.785
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…my little whore queen.</font>

908
01:33:06.498 --> 01:33:08.333
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">What queen-like behavior.</font>

909
01:33:10.043 --> 01:33:13.171
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Remove her from this chamber
before she infects us further…</font>

910
01:33:13.338 --> 01:33:16.341
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…with her inglorious and shabby self.</font>

911
01:33:23.181 --> 01:33:24.766
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">This will not be over quickly.</font>

912
01:33:26.100 --> 01:33:29.646
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You will not enjoy this.
I am not your queen.</font>

913
01:33:51.793 --> 01:33:53.711
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Traitor.</font>

914
01:33:54.254 --> 01:33:59.050
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Traitor! Traitor! Traitor!</font>

915
01:33:59.342 --> 01:34:01.594
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Traitor!</i></font>

916
01:34:38.631 --> 01:34:44.637
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Leonidas, my compliments
and congratulations.</font>

917
01:34:44.804 --> 01:34:48.474
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You surely have turned calamity
into victory.</font>

918
01:34:48.641 --> 01:34:51.644
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Despite your insufferable arrogance…</font>

919
01:34:51.811 --> 01:34:55.982
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…the god-king has come
to admire Spartan valor and fighting skill.</font>

920
01:34:56.733 --> 01:34:58.109
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You will make a mighty ally.</font>

921
01:34:58.276 --> 01:34:59.986
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Yield, Leonidas.</font>

922
01:35:01.154 --> 01:35:04.032
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Use your reason. Think of your men.</font>

923
01:35:06.868 --> 01:35:08.494
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">I beg you.</font>

924
01:35:09.078 --> 01:35:11.039
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Listen to your fellow Greek.</font>

925
01:35:11.205 --> 01:35:14.918
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">He can attest
to the divine one's generosity.</font>

926
01:35:15.084 --> 01:35:19.547
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Despite your several insults,
despite your horrid blasphemies…</font>

927
01:35:20.465 --> 01:35:23.635
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…the lord of hosts
is prepared to forgive all…</font>

928
01:35:23.885 --> 01:35:26.930
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…and more, to reward your service.</font>

929
01:35:27.180 --> 01:35:28.514
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You fight for your lands.</font>

930
01:35:29.224 --> 01:35:31.059
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Keep them.</font>

931
01:35:31.768 --> 01:35:33.728
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You fight for Sparta.</font>

932
01:35:33.895 --> 01:35:37.899
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">She will be wealthier and more powerful
than ever before.</font>

933
01:35:38.107 --> 01:35:40.026
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You fight for your kingship.</font>

934
01:35:40.944 --> 01:35:43.905
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You will be proclaimed warlord
of all Greece…</font>

935
01:35:44.072 --> 01:35:48.368
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…answerable only
to the one true master of the world.</font>

936
01:35:48.743 --> 01:35:53.498
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Leonidas, your victory will be complete…</font>

937
01:35:53.665 --> 01:35:56.250
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…if you but lay down your arms…</font>

938
01:35:56.417 --> 01:35:59.587
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…and kneel to holy Xerxes.</font>

939
01:36:30.076 --> 01:36:35.039
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>It's been more than 30 years
since the wolf in the winter cold.</i></font>

940
01:36:35.206 --> 01:36:39.752
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>And now, as then,
it's not fear that grips him…</i></font>

941
01:36:39.919 --> 01:36:45.091
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…only restlessness.
A heightened sense of things.</i></font>

942
01:36:45.883 --> 01:36:50.680
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>The seaborne breeze coolly kissing
the sweat at his chest and neck.</i></font>

943
01:36:50.847 --> 01:36:52.348
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Gulls cawing…</i></font>

944
01:36:52.515 --> 01:36:56.728
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…complaining even as they feast
on the thousands of floating dead.</i></font>

945
01:36:58.354 --> 01:37:03.401
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>The steady breathing
of the 300 at his back…</i></font>

946
01:37:04.193 --> 01:37:07.655
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…ready to die for him
without a moment's pause.</i></font>

947
01:37:10.241 --> 01:37:11.617
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Every one of them…</i></font>

948
01:37:13.077 --> 01:37:15.038
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…ready to die.</i></font>

949
01:37:30.553 --> 01:37:33.473
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>His helmet is stifling.</i></font>

950
01:37:54.160 --> 01:37:56.996
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>His shield is heavy.</i></font>

951
01:38:04.629 --> 01:38:05.963
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Your spear.</font>

952
01:38:14.806 --> 01:38:16.224
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">You there…</font>

953
01:38:16.641 --> 01:38:18.643
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…Ephialtes.</font>

954
01:38:23.773 --> 01:38:26.025
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">May you live forever.</font>

955
01:38:33.449 --> 01:38:35.743
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Leonidas, your spear.</font>

956
01:39:42.977 --> 01:39:44.562
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Stelios!</font>

957
01:39:54.572 --> 01:39:56.199
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Slaughter them!</font>

958
01:39:59.577 --> 01:40:01.162
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>His helmet was stifling.</i></font>

959
01:40:01.329 --> 01:40:04.457
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>It narrowed his vision,
and he must see far.</i></font>

960
01:40:05.750 --> 01:40:09.629
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>His shield was heavy.
It threw him off balance…</i></font>

961
01:40:09.795 --> 01:40:13.466
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…and his target is far away.</i></font>

962
01:41:18.030 --> 01:41:22.618
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>The old ones say we Spartans
are descended from Hercules himself.</i></font>

963
01:41:24.078 --> 01:41:28.416
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Bold Leonidas gives testament
to our bloodline.</i></font>

964
01:41:28.582 --> 01:41:32.712
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>His roar is long and loud.</i></font>

965
01:42:02.825 --> 01:42:04.410
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">My king.</font>

966
01:42:16.672 --> 01:42:20.301
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">It's an honor to die at your side.</font>

967
01:42:21.886 --> 01:42:26.390
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">It's an honor to have lived at yours.</font>

968
01:42:47.286 --> 01:42:49.413
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">My queen!</font>

969
01:42:57.630 --> 01:42:59.382
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">My wife.</font>

970
01:43:10.810 --> 01:43:12.603
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">My love.</font>

971
01:45:39.041 --> 01:45:41.168
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>"Remember us".</i></font>

972
01:45:42.836 --> 01:45:46.257
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>As simple an order as a king can give.</i></font>

973
01:45:47.842 --> 01:45:51.053
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>"Remember why we died".</i></font>

974
01:45:53.055 --> 01:45:57.101
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">For he did not wish tribute or song…</font>

975
01:45:58.936 --> 01:46:03.107
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…nor monuments,
nor poems of war and valor.</font>

976
01:46:05.985 --> 01:46:08.279
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">His wish was simple.</font>

977
01:46:13.659 --> 01:46:15.744
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">"Remember us"…</font>

978
01:46:16.787 --> 01:46:18.497
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…he said to me.</font>

979
01:46:20.165 --> 01:46:22.376
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>That was his hope.</i></font>

980
01:46:22.585 --> 01:46:26.297
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Should any free soul
come across that place…</i></font>

981
01:46:27.089 --> 01:46:30.426
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…in all the countless
centuries yet to be…</i></font>

982
01:46:30.843 --> 01:46:33.429
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…may all our voices…</i></font>

983
01:46:33.596 --> 01:46:37.641
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…whisper to you
from the ageless stones.</i></font>

984
01:46:38.642 --> 01:46:42.271
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>Go tell the Spartans, passerby…</i></font>

985
01:46:42.605 --> 01:46:48.485
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…that here, by Spartan law, we lie.</i></font>

986
01:46:51.238 --> 01:46:53.949
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>And so my king died…</i></font>

987
01:46:54.825 --> 01:46:57.453
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0"><i>…and my brothers died…</i></font>

988
01:46:59.830 --> 01:47:02.291
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…barely a year ago.</font>

989
01:47:06.211 --> 01:47:11.467
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Long I pondered my king's
cryptic talk of victory.</font>

990
01:47:11.675 --> 01:47:14.345
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Time has proven him wise.</font>

991
01:47:15.220 --> 01:47:18.265
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">For from free Greek to free Greek…</font>

992
01:47:18.432 --> 01:47:23.020
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…the word was spread
that bold Leonidas and his 300…</font>

993
01:47:23.187 --> 01:47:25.189
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…so far from home…</font>

994
01:47:25.356 --> 01:47:28.776
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…laid down their lives
not just for Sparta…</font>

995
01:47:28.942 --> 01:47:32.738
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…but for all Greece
and the promise this country holds.</font>

996
01:47:33.656 --> 01:47:38.702
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Now, here on this rugged patch of earth
called Plataea…</font>

997
01:47:38.869 --> 01:47:43.874
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…Xerxes' hordes face obliteration!</font>

998
01:47:45.542 --> 01:47:48.962
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Just there the barbarians huddle…</font>

999
01:47:49.129 --> 01:47:54.009
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…sheer terror gripping tight their hearts…</font>

1000
01:47:54.176 --> 01:47:56.053
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…with icy fingers…</font>

1001
01:47:56.220 --> 01:47:59.473
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…knowing full well
what merciless horrors they suffered…</font>

1002
01:47:59.640 --> 01:48:02.184
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…at the swords and spears of 300.</font>

1003
01:48:03.560 --> 01:48:09.149
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Yet they stare now across the plain
at 10,000 Spartans…</font>

1004
01:48:09.316 --> 01:48:12.611
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…commanding 30,000 free Greeks!</font>

1005
01:48:19.410 --> 01:48:23.330
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">The enemy outnumber us
a paltry three to one.</font>

1006
01:48:23.622 --> 01:48:25.624
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Good odds for any Greek.</font>

1007
01:48:26.333 --> 01:48:31.046
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">This day, we rescue a world
from mysticism and tyranny…</font>

1008
01:48:31.213 --> 01:48:35.592
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…and usher in a future
brighter than anything we can imagine.</font>

1009
01:48:40.013 --> 01:48:41.515
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">Give thanks, men…</font>

1010
01:48:42.224 --> 01:48:45.978
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">…to Leonidas and the brave 300.</font>

1011
01:48:46.145 --> 01:48:48.897
<font face="Perpetua" color="#c0c0c0">To victory!</font>

